lead_paragraph: Former Olympic champions Natalie Coughlin and Tyler Clary bid farewell at the U.S. swimming trials, although only Clary said he was retiring.

headline.print_headline: Coughlin and Clary Bid Farewell at US Olympic Swim Trials
